  <entry>
    <title>[Git]处理 GitHub - Failed to sync this branch 的问题</title>
    <link href="http://ted423.github.io/Code/Git/Failed%20to%20sync%20this%20branch/"/>
    <id>http://ted423.github.io/Code/Git/Failed%20to%20sync%20this%20branch/</id>
    <published>2021-08-05T12:39:16.993Z</published>
    <updated>2017-03-13T13:21:00.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>其实估计跟前段时间乱玩rebase有关,用 <code>git push</code>正常，但是sync就会提示”GitHub - Failed to sync this branch”</p><p>打开git shell<br>输入<code>git status</code></p><p>它会提示你原因<br>我这里提示是 “Could not open file .git/rebase-merge/done for reading: No such file or directory”</p><p>把rebase-merge整个删掉后就正常了</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;其实估计跟前段时间乱玩rebase有关,用 &lt;code&gt;git push&lt;/code&gt;正常，但是sync就会提示”GitHub - Failed to sync this branch”&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;打开git shell&lt;br&gt;输入&lt;code&gt;git status&lt;/c</summary>
      
    
    
    
